(3315,1,'2020-12-30 12:56:06','2020-12-30 12:56:06','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>[vc_row][vc_column][rev_slider_vc alias=\"landing-top\" enable_paspartu=\"no\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row content_placement=\"middle\" row_content_width=\"grid\" content_text_aligment=\"center\" css=\".vc_custom_1530002549898{padding-top: 152px !important;}\" anchor=\"section1\"][vc_column width=\"3/4\" offset=\"vc_col-lg-offset-0 vc_col-lg-5 vc_col-md-offset-0 vc_col-md-8 vc_col-sm-offset-0 vc_col-xs-12\"][edgtf_section_title type=\"standard\" position=\"left\" title_tag=\"h3\" disable_break_words=\"no\" text_font_weight=\"\" title=\"The Era of True Ownership\" title_break_words=\"4\" image=\"\" text=\"If its not in your Wallet, it is not your Asset. Traditional gaming gives you temporal ownership to your in-game assets, the moment you leave the game, asset\'s gone. CitizenFi gives players complete ownership of their in-game assets using blockchain technology. Every single item is a Non-Fungible Token (NFT) based on the Ethereum blockchain. You own one, it is permanently yours. You can sell it, gift it, stake it or use it as collateral.<br>As a token that is used to represent digital ownership, NFTs are rare gems and scarcely unique. Each NFT has it\'s own unique properties and multiple use case in the platform.\" holder_padding=\"0px\" text_margin=\"18px\" title_hightlight_words=\"5\"][vc_empty_space height=\"43px\"][edgtf_elements_holder holder_full_height=\"no\" number_of_columns=\"two-columns\" switch_to_one_column=\"680\" alignment_one_column=\"\"][edgtf_elements_holder_item item_padding_680=\"0 0 30px\"][edgtf_button text=\"Explore NFT\" target=\"_self\" icon_pack=\"\" font_weight=\"\" text_transform=\"\" link=\"http://localhost/wordpress/non-fungible\"][/edgtf_elements_holder_item][edgtf_elements_holder_item item_padding_680=\"0 0\"][edgtf_button type=\"outline\" text=\"Document\" target=\"_self\" icon_pack=\"\" font_weight=\"\" text_transform=\"\" link=\"https://docs.citizenfi.com\" padding=\"13px 62px\"][/edgtf_elements_holder_item][/edgtf_elements_holder][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\" offset=\"vc_col-lg-offset-0 vc_col-lg-7 vc_col-md-offset-0 vc_col-md-4 vc_col-sm-offset-0 vc_hidden-xs\"][vc_single_image image=\"3322\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_content_width=\"grid\" css=\".vc_custom_1529566860948{padding-top: 131px !important;padding-bottom: 180px !important;}\"][vc_column][edgtf_section_title type=\"standard\" position=\"center\" title_tag=\"\" disable_break_words=\"no\" separator_type=\"svg\" text_font_weight=\"\" title=\"NFT Ecosystem\" svg=\"\" text=\"There are vast numbers of unused in-game assets lying on players armory. Players are most likely not to use up to 70% of the assets in their armory throughout their session. Traditional gaming gives you no chance to sell it while other blockchain based games gives you option to sell it. CitizenFi gives you multiple options on what to do with your unused NFT as you might also need them in future.\"][vc_empty_space height=\"88px\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][edgtf_icon_with_text type=\"icon-top\" icon_pack=\"font_awesome\" fa_icon=\"fa fa-gamepad\" title_tag=\"\" title=\"Play\" text=\"As an in-game asset, NFT can be used to play the CitizenFI FPS game on mobile and PC.\" icon_color=\"#1c97af\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][edgtf_icon_with_text type=\"icon-top\" icon_pack=\"font_awesome\" fa_icon=\"fa fa-shopping-bag\" title_tag=\"\" title=\"Trade\" text=\"NFTs can be withdrawn from the game and freely traded on any NFT marketplace without restrictions.\" icon_color=\"#a515a3\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][edgtf_icon_with_text type=\"icon-top\" icon_pack=\"font_awesome\" fa_icon=\"fa fa-handshake\" title_tag=\"\" title=\"Collateral\" text=\"NFT can also be used as a form of Collateral in CitizenFi lending protocol.\" icon_color=\"#dd0404\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][edgtf_icon_with_text type=\"icon-top\" icon_pack=\"font_awesome\" fa_icon=\"fa fa-leaf\" title_tag=\"\" title=\"Farm\" text=\"Farm digital currency by staking your unused NFT in decentralized farming pools.\" icon_color=\"#129b00\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_empty_space height=\"100px\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"3193\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"right\" style=\"vc_box_rounded\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][edgtf_section_title type=\"standard\" position=\"center\" title_tag=\"\" disable_break_words=\"no\" title=\"ABOUT\" image=\"\"][edgtf_section_title type=\"standard\" position=\"center\" title_tag=\"\" disable_break_words=\"no\" separator_type=\"svg\" text_font_weight=\"\" title=\"THE GAME\" svg=\"\" text=\"When Earth is faced with an invasion by alien force, Government of the world needs to come together to prevent colonization and destruction of human heritage but it is a small group, a few escapees from San Francisco, who were able to flee colonization camp that will take on the colonialist. their mission is to destroy the plans of the colonialist, liberate cities one by one and preserve humanity.\"][vc_empty_space][vc_btn title=\"Explore More\" style=\"outline\" shape=\"square\" color=\"danger\" size=\"lg\" align=\"center\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Fwordpress%2Fabout-the-game|title:About%20The%20Game||\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_empty_space height=\"100px\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][edgtf_section_title type=\"standard\" position=\"center\" title_tag=\"\" disable_break_words=\"no\" separator_type=\"svg\" text_font_weight=\"\" title=\"Reshaping The NFT Industry\" svg=\"\" text=\"The NFT industry although very lucrative, it is also plague with a particular issue - Liquidation. As a digital assets, Current NFTs has no particular value as the assets belongs to the owner and the owner has the right to resell at any price he/she wants. This can be good but also has its own negative effects. NFT can be bought for a high price but the chance of the buyer reselling for same price or higher it\'s rare. The option of instant liquidation is also non in existence, the owner needs to look for a buyer to be able to liquidate the assets. We have decided to use a new mechanism to solve this issues.\"][vc_empty_space height=\"60px\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][edgtf_icon_with_text type=\"icon-left\" icon_pack=\"font_awesome\" fa_icon=\"fab fa-ethereum\" icon_size=\"edgtf-icon-large\" title_tag=\"\" title=\"Face Value\" text=\"Each NFT will be minted with a Face Value. Tokens will be locked on smart contract to mint each NFT face value. The face value of each NFT will be equivalent to the locked token. The owner can resell for any price so desired as long as the buyer is willing to pay.\" icon_color=\"#17c900\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][edgtf_icon_with_text type=\"icon-left\" icon_pack=\"font_awesome\" fa_icon=\"fa fa-fire\" icon_size=\"edgtf-icon-large\" title_tag=\"\" title=\"Liquidation\" text=\"NFT can be instantly liquidated if not sold. The owner can burn the NFT to obtain the Face value that was locked to mint the asset. While measuring the asset with it\'s face value, CitizenFi will allow players borrow from pools with their NFT as collateral.\" icon_color=\"#dd0000\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_content_width=\"grid\" disable_background_image=\"\" css=\".vc_custom_1528277929528{padding-top: 142px !important;padding-bottom: 140px !important;}\" simple_background_image=\"225\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner content_text_aligment=\"center\"][vc_column_inner][rev_slider slidertitle=\"guns\" alias=\"landing-bottom-1\"][vc_empty_space height=\"150px\"][edgtf_section_title type=\"standard\" position=\"center\" title_tag=\"\" disable_break_words=\"no\" separator_type=\"svg\" text_font_weight=\"\" title=\"Multiple Platforms\" text=\"Are you a 