in existence, the owner needs to look for a buyer to be able to liquidate the assets. We have decided to use a new mechanism to solve this issues.\"][vc_empty_space height=\"60px\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][edgtf_icon_with_text type=\"icon-left\" icon_pack=\"font_awesome\" fa_icon=\"fab fa-ethereum\" icon_size=\"edgtf-icon-large\" title_tag=\"\" title=\"Face Value\" text=\"Each NFT will be minted with a Face Value. Tokens will be locked on smart contract to mint each NFT face value. The face value of each NFT will be equivalent to the locked token. The owner can resell for any price so desired as long as the buyer is willing to pay.\" icon_color=\"#17c900\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][edgtf_icon_with_text type=\"icon-left\" icon_pack=\"font_awesome\" fa_icon=\"fa fa-fire\" icon_size=\"edgtf-icon-large\" title_tag=\"\" title=\"Liquidation\" text=\"NFT can be instantly liquidated if not sold. The owner can burn the NFT to obtain the Face value that was locked to mint the asset. While measuring the asset with it\'s face value, CitizenFi will allow players borrow from pools with their NFT as collateral.\" icon_color=\"#dd0000\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_content_width=\"grid\" disable_background_image=\"1024\" simple_background_image=\"513\" simple_background_color=\"#17161a\" el_class=\"eao\" el_id=\"eao\"][vc_column offset=\"vc_col-lg-offset-0 vc_col-lg-12 vc_col-md-offset-0 vc_col-md-12 vc_col-sm-offset-0 vc_col-xs-12\"][edgtf_elements_holder holder_full_height=\"no\" number_of_columns=\"two-columns\" switch_to_one_column=\"1024\" alignment_one_column=\"\"][edgtf_elements_holder_item item_padding_769_1024=\"19.5% 27% 19% 0\" item_padding_681_768=\"25% 27% 24.5% 0\" item_padding_680=\"51% 0 50.5% 0\" item_padding_1025_1366=\"27.5% 19% 28.5% 0\" item_padding=\"25% 19% 26.5% 0\"